  "content": "<p data-pid=\"O9xOA5by\">这个其实挺简单的，严格上来说，SuperMemo 没有特殊的填空卡片。所谓挖空，其实就是一张正面问题、反面答案的问答卡片，只不过正面把挖空内容替换成了 <b>[...]</b></p><p data-pid=\"sXYOmt20\">所以，想要一卡多空，就是把多处挖空内容替换成 <b>[...] </b>即可</p><p data-pid=\"no2pIC8r\">光靠文字描述有些抽象，举个例子好了，假设以下内容是摘录出来的片段，需要同时挖多个空：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e34cf93f6e4de2d47c8d48e869b9e0bb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-e34cf93f6e4de2d47c8d48e869b9e0bb\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d4341748793dacb03366808dde3db67_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e34cf93f6e4de2d47c8d48e869b9e0bb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;960&#39; height=&#39;794&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-e34cf93f6e4de2d47c8d48e869b9e0bb\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d4341748793dacb03366808dde3db67_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e34cf93f6e4de2d47c8d48e869b9e0bb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e34cf93f6e4de2d47c8d48e869b9e0bb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"VNVU-bj3\">首先，按照常规挖空的方式，选中一处要挖空的内容，使用 alt + z 挖空：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-79ac05fb5f9ff1a781d63c40d7de48f9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-79ac05fb5f9ff1a781d63c40d7de48f9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9588b5cca0dc4367e50fa597a842e3cd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-79ac05fb5f9ff1a781d63c40d7de48f9_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;960&#39; height=&#39;794&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-79ac05fb5f9ff1a781d63c40d7de48f9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9588b5cca0dc4367e50fa597a842e3cd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-79ac05fb5f9ff1a781d63c40d7de48f9_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-79ac05fb5f9ff1a781d63c40d7de48f9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"vZmXeurt\">可以看到，A 已经被标记，如果我们此时再对 B、C、D 做同样的操作，就会派生多张卡片，分别以B、C、D为挖空内容。这与我们一卡多空的需求不符</p><p data-pid=\"R7bIVkyy\">所以，这时我们不能依靠 alt + z，要手动进行挖空，该怎么操作呢？</p><p data-pid=\"zhZNDngG\">先使用 alt + ← 或</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-58a18c445a8004746b04e8c90f0c15fe_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"457\" data-rawheight=\"102\" data-original-token=\"v2-58a18c445a8004746b04e8c90f0c15fe\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1c3ca034d9c32c34c65ff92f82a94299_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"457\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-58a18c445a8004746b04e8c90f0c15fe_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;457&#39; height=&#39;102&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"457\" data-rawheight=\"102\" data-original-token=\"v2-58a18c445a8004746b04e8c90f0c15fe\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1c3ca034d9c32c34c65ff92f82a94299_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"457\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-58a18c445a8004746b04e8c90f0c15fe_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-58a18c445a8004746b04e8c90f0c15fe_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"2thsDwLt\">回到以 A 为挖空内容的问答卡片：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9cef19bd136488b526c31be66f88822b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-9cef19bd136488b526c31be66f88822b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-839d2d11bd93b7c2435508cfd4c37718_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9cef19bd136488b526c31be66f88822b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;960&#39; height=&#39;794&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-9cef19bd136488b526c31be66f88822b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-839d2d11bd93b7c2435508cfd4c37718_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9cef19bd136488b526c31be66f88822b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9cef19bd136488b526c31be66f88822b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"PYndFdK7\">然后，我们把 B、C、D 都复制粘贴到 A 所在的答案框中（为了方便区分，我输入 | 作为分隔符）：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e080621b43eb45fa0889f27700e63516_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-e080621b43eb45fa0889f27700e63516\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e13dae002207cdf172e10ee0441ac138_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e080621b43eb45fa0889f27700e63516_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;960&#39; height=&#39;794&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-e080621b43eb45fa0889f27700e63516\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e13dae002207cdf172e10ee0441ac138_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e080621b43eb45fa0889f27700e63516_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e080621b43eb45fa0889f27700e63516_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"ZzJvxoyE\">然后，复制问题框中的 [...]，粘贴覆盖问题中的 B、C、D：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-abc95f41737cde5acdc61d30393bbc1d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-abc95f41737cde5acdc61d30393bbc1d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-6138cce1faf4c2ba57fe80a7d413f52a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-abc95f41737cde5acdc61d30393bbc1d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;960&#39; height=&#39;794&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"794\" data-original-token=\"v2-abc95f41737cde5acdc61d30393bbc1d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-6138cce1faf4c2ba57fe80a7d413f52a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-abc95f41737cde5acdc61d30393bbc1d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-abc95f41737cde5acdc61d30393bbc1d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Hc1rTPgY\">大功告成！</p><p data-pid=\"KnDmYrVz\">是不是很简单（溜了溜了</p>",
